metadata.name: Gnarly #16
metadata.description:
Gnarly is an interactive nft game.

Fly across the city with your hoverboard and avoid the obstacles.

Each iteration will generate a totally different character to play!

Don't forget to collect the coins and eat pizza to recover your health!
You can also collect the sandclocks to slow down the time!

Use the touch/mouse or enter/space keys to jump (you can even double jump!)

Press S to save a screenshot of the game!

metadata.name: Vents #61
metadata.description:
Near the start of December @Studio Yorktown launched his "Studio Yorktown Color Town Hall" library of wonderful colour palettes.

"You know what this Town Hall needs?" I asked no one in particular, "Vents!". Besides, what's more Christmassy than a good old vent?

Some nice soothing gradients, with a selection of innies and outies, structure, form, and sometimes sharp edges. I humbly suggest aiming to get a set of three üòÅ

Thank you for everything fxhash in 2022, looking forwards to 2023!

READ MORE: https://www.fxhash.xyz/article/vents

INSTRUCTIONS ::

h - Toggle high-res
n - toggle noise on/off
s - Download and save image

PRINTING INSTRUCTIONS ::

High-res will output a 8,192 x 8,192 image, at 300dpi it should print at...

27.3 x 27.3 inches
69.3 x 69.3 cm

metadata.name: Touching #151
metadata.description:
A confirmation of reality... but is it, or is it not?

For some it is, for some it is not.

* * *

To a great new year together, full of touching loved ones, goodness, happiness and dreams.

Press S to save as PNG. To save a larger image, open live view, add "&s=WIDTH_IN_PIXELS" to the end of the URL, press Enter and then press S.

Artwork by: yenren / twitter.com/yenrenART

metadata.name: Line art #zentangle2 #20
metadata.description:
Life was a point!
In Big Bang!
A point that expanded
He formed the lines
and made the world
The world in which we are the size of a point!
Maybe even smaller!


Play with lines
This collection is the result of my playing with the lines I drew with the tablet.
This set has 9 layers
The first layer contains the background
The second layer of lines
The third layer of flowers and plants
The fourth layer of the lines I drew with the tablet is 22 different images in zentangle style
The fifth layer of flowers and plants
Sixth layers of grass
The seventh layer of flowers
The eighth layer of some special flowers and plants with less repetition in the collection
The ninth layer of the cover

This is the last of my collection in 2022!
I hope we start the new year with energy
Forward to 2023
Mint opening time 20:23!
